      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "イヤです～！　寒いです～！",
      "startTime": 1.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.7635145902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……と言いつつ、よく自分から外出する\n決心がついたな。どういう心境の変化だ？",
      "startTime": 8.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7718593995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、こころはファンの子達に出会って\n北海道って寒いけど、人は温かいなって思いまして",
      "startTime": 16.1750114759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "よそ者に優しいというか……昨日のかまくらだって\n見知らぬこころ達をにこにこ～って受け入れてくれて",
      "startTime": 26.1750114759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5257134834
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "だから、練習の空き時間には出来るだけ\n北海道の人達と触れ合おうかな～……なんて",
      "startTime": 33.6750114759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.1239670513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "こころ達が歌を届ける相手のことを\nもっと良く知りたいと思ったんです",
      "startTime": 40.8750114759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そして、相手を想う気持ちを、曲に乗せて……\n今のこころに出来る、最高のステージを届けたいんです",
      "startTime": 47.9416781426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4977066753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか。それがこころなりの\nファンへの向き合い方なんだな",
      "startTime": 55.1999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "って何言わせるんですか。{user}さんは\n聞き上手だから、余計なことまで喋っちゃいます",
      "startTime": 60.7364613216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6682738064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "今話したことは、ここだけにしておいて下さいね？",
      "startTime": 64.6682738064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.8426502782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、分かった。それじゃ街巡り、俺も付き合うよ\nどこに行くんだ？",
      "startTime": 74.0333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "今日は公園に向かおうかなと",
      "startTime": 75.5252806582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.551539087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なんでまた北海道に来て公園なんだ？\n他にも観光名所が沢山あるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 81.5999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "それが、昨日ホテルで調べたんですけど\n北海道の冬の公園って凄いんですよ～",
      "startTime": 87.9290880839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.383462985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "スキー場じゃないのにスキーやソリで遊べますし\nかまくらの中でライトアップとか～",
      "startTime": 95.2957547505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "有名どころだと、今の時期は\n雪像を建てたりもするそうなんです",
      "startTime": 100.3290916443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.2660288648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "へえ……昨日の今日で、よく調べたな\n内容がレジャー方面に偏ってるのが気にはなるけど",
      "startTime": 107.4999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3660288648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "一応言っておきますけど～\n遊びに行く訳じゃないですからね？",
      "startTime": 114.0624249776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "北海道のみなさんの日常に触れたいから\n観光地じゃなく、普通の公園に行くんですよ",
      "startTime": 120.195758311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7904976365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、よく考えてるんだな",
      "startTime": 123.7904976365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "あ、公園が近いみたいですね、人が増えてきました",
      "startTime": 127.1701121964,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5855.326636600012,
          "startTime": 133.025438833
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-snow-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5988.6620045000145,
          "startTime": 133.1587742009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7921075342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "おお、賑わってるな\n公園なのにスキーのレンタルをやってるみたいだ",
      "startTime": 136.866663615,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-snow-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15666.6697183,
          "startTime": 152.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～、公園の中をスキーで歩くんですね\n北海道らしいですね～。ここは挑戦あるのみです",
      "startTime": 144.5289577008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.2876802601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "転んでケガだけはしないでくれよ？",
      "startTime": 149.2876802601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "startTime": 154.2911052066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.3244273502
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.3244273502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、もうすぐ本番だけど、寒さは平気か？",
      "startTime": 156.3244273502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です～。北海道の人の温もりを知りましたから\n……歩行スキーは散々でしたけど",
      "startTime": 165.2923683487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.334041659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは沢山転んでましたね～",
      "startTime": 168.334041659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "自分は全然転んでないみたいに言わないでくれ\nこころも同じくらい沢山転んでただろ",
      "startTime": 175.9333221437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.0088425319
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
